                            <customfieldvalue>TOKENIZE now can take an optional second argument as delimiter.&lt;br/&gt;
Usage:&lt;br/&gt;
{code}&lt;br/&gt;
a = load &amp;#39;data&amp;#39; as (f1:chararray);&lt;br/&gt;
b = foreach a TOKENIZE (f1,&amp;#39;||&amp;#39;);&lt;br/&gt;
dump b;&lt;br/&gt;
{code}</customfieldvalue>

